\subsection{Results: Partitioning of Variance and RM-ANOVA}
The RM-ANOVA partitions total variation ($SST$) into between-TTO effects ($SSM$), between-subject differences ($SSS$), and residual error ($SSE$).
\begin{equation}
    SST = SSM + SSS + SSE \approx 7.8468
\end{equation}

