\subsection{Results and Statistical Interpretation}
The analysis of Skubal's 2024 season revealed a variance of $497.73$ with runners on ($n=186$) and $461.62$ with the bases empty ($n=367$). This resulted in an observed volatility statistic of $\tau_{vol} = 36.11$. 

